18#include <string>
19#include <utility>
20#include <stdexcept>
21#include "ByteArray.h"
22#include "DMSymbolShape.h"
23#include "DMSymbolInfo.h"
24#include "ZXStrConvWorkaround.h"
25
26namespace ZXing {
27namespace DataMatrix {
28
29class SymbolInfo;
30
31class EncoderContext
32{
33 std::string _msg;
34 SymbolShape _shape = SymbolShape::NONE;
35 int _minWidth = -1;
36 int _minHeight = -1;
37 int _maxWidth = -1;
38 int _maxHeight = -1;
39 ByteArray _codewords;
40 int _pos = 0;
41 int _newEncoding = -1;
42 const SymbolInfo* _symbolInfo = nullptr;
43 int _skipAtEnd = 0;
44
45public:
46 explicit EncoderContext(std::string&& msg) : _msg(std::move(msg)) { _codewords.reserve(_msg.length()); }
47
48 EncoderContext(const EncoderContext &) = delete; // avoid copy by mistake
49
50 void setSymbolShape(SymbolShape shape) {
51 _shape = shape;
52 }
53
54 void setSizeConstraints(int minWidth, int minHeight, int maxWidth, int maxHeight) {
55 _minWidth = minWidth;
56 _minHeight = minHeight;
57 _maxWidth = maxWidth;
58 _maxHeight = maxHeight;
59 }
60
61 const std::string& message() const {
62 return _msg;
63 }
64
65 void setSkipAtEnd(int count) {
66 _skipAtEnd = count;
67 }
68
69 int currentPos() const {
70 return _pos;
71 }
72
73 void setCurrentPos(int pos) {
74 _pos = pos;
75 }
76
77 int currentChar() const {
78 return _msg.at(_pos) & 0xff;
79 }
80
81 int nextChar() const {
82 return _msg.at(_pos + 1) & 0xff;
83 }
84
85 const ByteArray& codewords() const {
86 return _codewords;
87 }
88
89 int codewordCount() const {
90 return (int)_codewords.size();
91 }
92
93 void addCodeword(uint8_t codeword) {
94 _codewords.push_back(codeword);
95 }
96
97 void setNewEncoding(int encoding) {
98 _newEncoding = encoding;
99 }
100
101 void clearNewEncoding() {
102 _newEncoding = -1;
103 }
104
105 int newEncoding() const {
106 return _newEncoding;
107 }
108
109 bool hasMoreCharacters() const {
110 return _pos < totalMessageCharCount();
111 }
112
113 int totalMessageCharCount() const {
114 return static_cast<int>(_msg.length() - _skipAtEnd);
115 }
116
117 int remainingCharacters() const {
118 return totalMessageCharCount() - _pos;
119 }
120
121 const SymbolInfo* updateSymbolInfo(int len) {
122 if (_symbolInfo == nullptr || len > _symbolInfo->dataCapacity()) {
123 _symbolInfo = SymbolInfo::Lookup(len, _shape, _minWidth, _minHeight, _maxWidth, _maxHeight);
124 if (_symbolInfo == nullptr) {
125 throw std::invalid_argument("Can't find a symbol arrangement that matches the message. Data codewords: " + std::to_string(len));
126 }
127 }
128 return _symbolInfo;
129 }
130
131 void resetSymbolInfo() {
132 _symbolInfo = nullptr;
133 }
134
135 const SymbolInfo* symbolInfo() const {
136 return _symbolInfo;
137 }
138};
139
140} // DataMatrix
141} // ZXing
142
